OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed at school
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith attempted murder and possession
OL,8,Fof a knife on a school premises after
OL,9,Fa teenage girl was stabbed at Thorpe
OL,10,FSt Andrew School on Wednesday, Norfolk
OL,11,Fpolice has said.
OL,13,FThe girl was taken to hospital with
OL,14,Fminor injuries after the attack at
OL,15,FThorpe St Andrew School, which
OL,16,Fhappened around 10.24am on Wednesday.
OL,17,FShe was released on Thursday.
OL,19,FPupils were put into lockdown in their
OL,20,Fclassrooms after the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
