PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773399918
OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed at school
OL,6,FThorpe St Andrew School said on
OL,7,FThursday that staff "remained calm"
OL,8,Fthroughout "a prolonged and
OL,9,Funderstandably distressing situation".
OL,11,FIt added that the teenage girl was
OL,12,F"doing well" and would be welcomed
OL,13,F"back to school when she is ready".
OL,15,FA 15-year-old white British boy was
OL,16,Farrested nearby on suspicion of
OL,17,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,18,Fintent and was taken to Wymondham
OL,19,Fpolice investigation centre for
OL,20,Fquestioning.
