FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773399918
OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed at school
OL,6,F"Throughout a prolonged and
OL,7,Funderstandably distressing situation,
OL,8,Fstaff remained calm, focusing on
OL,9,Fsupporting and protecting the students
OL,10,Fin their care, who in turn showed
OL,11,Fgreat maturity and composure.
OL,13,F"As the situation unfolded, staff
OL,14,Fneeded to respond to the needs of the
OL,15,Fparticular students in front of them
OL,16,Fand adapt their approach accordingly,
OL,17,Falways with the priority of keeping
OL,18,Feveryone safe and supported.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773399918
OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed at school
OL,6,F"We understand how worrying this event
OL,7,Fwas for families and want to thank our
OL,8,Fstudents who coped so well. We have
OL,9,Fshared a range of support measures we
OL,10,Fare providing for students, families
OL,11,Fand the community for as long as it is
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,F"We sincerely hope that we, and indeed
OL,15,Fevery other school across the country,
OL,16,Fnever have to put these protocols into
OL,17,Fpractice again and would like to thank
OL,18,Fthe emergency services for their
OL,19,Fexpertise and response yesterday."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
