OL,3,CBoy, 15, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed at school
OL,6,FThorpe St Andrew School, which was
OL,7,Frated as good in its 2025 Ofsted
OL,8,Finspection, is an 11-to-18 mixed
OL,9,Fsecondary school which also includes a
OL,10,Fsixth form.
OL,12,FNorfolk Police added the incident is
OL,13,Fnot believed to be linked to a hate
OL,14,Fcrime reported at the school last week
OL,15,Fafter allegations of antisemitic
OL,16,Fchanting during a football match
OL,17,Finvolving a Jewish school.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
